<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mryḥ ạltʿạby̱</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ṣwth lsh byndh mn snyn
 tʿạlwạ ạ̹lyã yạ kl ạlmtʿbyn)2
 (lw tʿbạn ʿndh ạlsẖfạʾ .. lạ̉y jrḥ wạ̉y dạʾ
 wạ̹n ḍạʿ ḥlmk ywm wtạh .. htlạqy njạẗ
 lw yạ̉sạn mn nfsk rwḥ
 qwl lh yạ ạ̉bwyạ ạ̉nạ ʿndy jrwḥ
 mstnyk tyjy wbạlrwḥ .. tdyny ḥyạẗ)2
 ạlqrạr- (hw mryḥ ạltʿạby̱ .. wạlnạs ạlgẖlạbẗ
 byḥwl ạlkậbẗ .. lạ̉gẖạny wạ̉frạḥ)2
 2- (ṣwth lsh byndh mn zmạn
 myn mḥtạj lslạm mḥtạj lạ̉mạn)2
 (lw tạyh msẖ lạqy ṭryq .. kl ḥyạtk hm wḍyq
 wsṭ bḥwr ạldnyạ gẖryq .. fy tʿb wsrạb
 lw btdwr mn snyn
 ʿly̱ ạ̉frạḥ bdl ạlạ̉nyn
 lw nfsk mạtkwnsẖ ḥzyn .. ạ̹ftḥ lh ạlbạb)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>11099</hymn_number>
</song>